init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see a small bee, not much bigger than your thumb.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's a little black and yellow striped bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's eyes are a bright red and it has a small crown on its head.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's wings are a dark black and it's body is a light yellow.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's small little arms are wrapped around your shoulder and it's legs are wrapped around your neck.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You realize that this is a queen bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've never seen one before, but you've heard about them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've heard that they are the most powerful of all the bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are the ones who control the hive and they are the ones who give orders.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've also heard that they are extremely rare and that they are the most powerful of all the bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've also heard that they are extremely protective of their hive and that they will do anything to protect it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You think to yourself, "What do I do?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I can't just let it stay on me like this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's going to sting me and I'm going to die."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You try to shake it off, but it doesn't budge.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You try to get it off, but it won't budge.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to panic and you start to sweat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to get nervous and your heart starts to beat faster and faster.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to feel a little dizzy and you start to get a little light headed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to feel a little nauseous and you start to feel a little sick to your stomach.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to feel a little weak and you start to feel a little woozy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to feel a little hot and you start to feel a little cold.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You start to feel a little shaky and you start to feel a little weak.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran and ran

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I also made sure i always wore long pants and long sleeves when i went out and i also made sure i always wore a hat and gloves.
